				<td colspan="2"><span>I remember stumbling across a link to some good fantasy novels with bards prevalent.. but I stupidly did not bookmark it.  I've been googling and searching this site all morning, and I've found nothing.
<br />

<br />
I'm feeling un-inspired.  I've been spinning my wheels at level 53 for FAR too long now... I need something to get myself passionate about being a bard again.
<br />

<br />
Fellow bards - give me some suggestions on some inspiring bardly books!
<br />
</span></td>
