				<td colspan="2"><span>
<br />
Tales of the Bard
<br />

<br />

<br />
It's a trilogy.  I read it about 10 years ago.  I forgot who
<br />
wrote it, but the story made such an impact on me that when
<br />
EQ came out, I had no choice but to be a bard.
<br />

<br />
'Stuce
<br />

<br />
edit: looked up a little bit online and found that the author is
<br />
Michael Scott.  The first book was &quot;Magician's Law&quot;, and the
<br />
third book was &quot;Death's Law&quot;, can't find title for second book.</span></td>
